node.text: We lost Aaron in 2018 to suicide. Over the past years since that tragic day, we’ve learned that struggles with mental health are far too common... we hope and pray this collaboration touches the lives of even just one precious soul 🙏🏻

node.text: I don’t even know where to begin....from seeing your heartbeat for the first time to seeing you dance around in mommy’s belly... we are truly blessed and this is only the beginning!! Little man, you have the best mommy already and I can’t wait to be your dad! We are so humbled by this gift God has given us. We love you already, buddy!!

I’m teaming up with Intuit @Quickbooks to celebrate my favorite small businesses as they recover and prosper from the tough past year. 

For the best haircut in southern New Jersey, check out Christian Tipton, the Owner of @razorsedgebarbers. They’ll have you looking your very best!  Prices are great and the laughs and quality conversations I have there make it all the more fun. I’ve been going to @razorsedgebarbers for years and they cut it exactly how I like every time! Christian’s one of the best dudes I know! If you’re in the area, go show them some love! Thanks for the help @Quickbooks! #BackSmallBiz #ad
